{"name":"ウィリアム・T・スピアーズ","nameCn":"威廉·T·史皮尔斯","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/m/8d/db/26706_crt_DsRHY.jpg","info":"<li><span>简体中文名: </span>威廉·T·史皮尔斯</li><li><span>别名: </span>威廉·T·史皮爾斯</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>William T. Spears</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>ウィル</li><li><span>性别: </span>男</li>","detail":"死神派遣協会管理課の死神。<br /><br />簡稱威廉。死神派遣協會管理課的死神。<br />戴眼鏡的男人。個性冷漠、認真的公務員類型。口頭禪是「絕不接受無薪加班。」死神鐮刀是可伸縮的高枝剪。<br />稱惡魔（賽巴斯欽）是會寄生在人類身上的「害蟲」。<br />對惡魔極度厭惡，認為他們就像烏鴉一般，沒有節制的獵食靈魂。馬戲團中的偽名是舒茲（SUIT）。（義為上班族，加入馬戲團是為了審核JOKER和凱爾文男爵，以及其他遭綁架的孩童靈魂。）<br />嚴重近視。在被賽巴斯欽打掉眼鏡後，因為近視還指著空氣罵羅納德。<br />在《Ciel in wonderland》（謝爾的奇幻仙境）飾演三月兔。","jobs":[{"href":"/subject/9737","name":"黒執事II OVA","nameCn":"黑执事II OVA","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/ce/46/9737_2Ux6E.jpg","staff":"配角","cast":"杉山紀彰","castHref":"/person/4578","castTag":"CV","castCover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/s/37/bd/4578_prsn_NKnxc.jpg"},{"href":"/subject/1748","name":"黒執事II","nameCn":"黑执事II","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/54/e3/1748_fKaeF.jpg","staff":"配角","cast":"杉山紀彰","castHref":"/person/4578","castTag":"CV","castCover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/s/37/bd/4578_prsn_NKnxc.jpg"},{"href":"/subject/883","name":"黒執事","nameCn":"黑执事","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/21/0f/883_9w87Y.jpg","staff":"配角","cast":"杉山紀彰","castHref":"/person/4578","castTag":"CV","castCover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/s/37/bd/4578_prsn_NKnxc.jpg"},{"href":"/subject/9698","name":"黒執事","nameCn":"黑执事","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/fc/2d/9698_6D9Pw.jpg","staff":"配角","cast":"","castHref":"","castTag":"","castCover":""},{"href":"/subject/100526","name":"黒執事 Book of Circus","nameCn":"黑执事 马戏团篇","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/38/ae/100526_Q0BET.jpg","staff":"配角","cast":"杉山紀彰","castHref":"/person/4578","castTag":"CV","castCover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/s/37/bd/4578_prsn_NKnxc.jpg"},{"href":"/subject/148389","name":"黒執事 Book of the Atlantic","nameCn":"黑执事 豪华客船篇","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/cb/85/148389_Kn5sW.jpg","staff":"配角"